cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper presents an automatic repair tool for formatting-related errors in software projects. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the tool is dedicated to fixing errors raised by Checkstyle, a format checker for Java. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the tool uses machine learning to predict repairs for formatting errors. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper discusses the use of machine learning for automatic code repair. 
- cs.SD (Software Development) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper focuses on improving code readability and quality through automatic formatting repair.
